Canadian actor Ryan Reynolds received a star on Hollywood s Walk of Fame. The 40-year-old, accompanied by his wife, American actress Blake Lively, and their two young daughters, recalled visiting Hollywood with one of his brothers 15 years ago and being in awe of all the legends immortalised along the iconic avenue. For me to have my name among them is beyond anything I could ever imagine, said Reynolds, who was nominated earlier this week for a Golden Globe award for his performance in Deadpool. A native of Vancouver, Reynolds has starred in a number of films based on comic books. AFP More news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.